OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FApple announces buy now,   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpay later, among iOS 16    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fplans                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Apple is planning a buy now, pay later 
OL,6, (BNPL) service as part of its new      
OL,7, operating system, iOS 16.              
OL,9,FApple Pay Later will allow users in the
OL,10,FUS to spread the cost of a purchase    
OL,11,Finto four payments over six weeks,     
OL,12,Fwithout paying interest or fees.       
OL,14,FIt forms part of a range of new iPhone 
OL,15,Ffeatures, including the ability to edit
OL,16,FiMessages and a feature intended to    
OL,17,Fhelp people in abusive relationships.  
OL,19,FThe features were unveiled at WWDC, the
OL,20,Ffirm's annual developers' conference.  
